programme.desc: When the Las Vegas revue she has headlined for decades announces it will soon close, showgirl Shelly must plan for her future.

programme.title: One of Them Days
programme.desc: When her boyfriend takes her rent money, Alyssa and her roommate race against the clock to avoid eviction and keep their friendship intact.

programme.title: MaXXXine
programme.desc: Aspiring movie star and hustler Maxine Minx finally gets her big break. But as a mysterious killer stalks the starlets of 1980s Hollywood, a trail of blood threatens to reveal her sinister past.

During the World Cup final between Argentina and Holland, in times of military dictatorship, a group of torturers kidnap a group of young people. What begins as an inhumane interrogation turns into hell as the wrong group has been kidnapped.

programme.title: The Exorcist: The Version Youve Never Seen
programme.desc: When a mysterious entity possesses a young girl, her mother seeks the help of two Catholic priests to save her life.

programme.title: Lady Bird
programme.desc: A teenager (Saoirse Ronan) navigates a loving but turbulent relationship with her strong-willed mother (Laurie Metcalf) over the course of an eventful and poignant senior year of high school.

programme.title: The Color Purple
programme.desc: Torn apart from her sister and her children, Celie faces many hardships, including an abusive husband. With support from a singer and her stepdaughter, she ultimately finds extraordinary strength in the unbreakable bonds of a new kind of sisterhood.

programme.title: Between the Temples
programme.desc: A cantor in a crisis of faith finds his world turned upside down when his grade school music teacher reenters his life as his new adult bat mitzvah student.

programme.title: Manchester by the Sea
programme.desc: After his older brother passes away, Lee Chandler is forced to return home to care for his 16-year-old nephew. There, he is compelled to deal with a tragic past that separated him from his family and the community where he was born and raised.

programme.title: Triangle of Sadness
programme.desc: Two models and a cleaning lady become stranded on a desert island with a group of billionaires.

programme.title: Destination Wedding
programme.desc: Wedding guests Frank and Lindsay discover that they have a lot in common -- they dont like the bride, the groom, the ceremony, themselves or each other.

programme.title: Kneecap
programme.desc: When fate brings a Belfast teacher into the orbit of self-confessed "lowlife scum" Naoise and Liam g, the needle drops on a hip-hop act like no other. Rapping in their native Irish language, they soon lead a movement to save their mother tongue.

programme.title: Arrival
programme.desc: A linguistics professor (Amy Adams) leads an elite team of investigators in a race against time to communicate with extraterrestrial visitors.

programme.title: Los Horrores de Caddo Lake
programme.desc: When an 8-year-old girl mysteriously vanishes, a series of past deaths and disappearances start to link together, forever altering a broken familys history.

programme.title: ngela Diniz: Murdered and Convicted
programme.desc: A prominent figure in Minas Gerais high society during the 1970s, ngela Diniz dared to defy norms and experience intense love until she was murdered by her partner, Doca Street.

programme.title: The Outrun
programme.desc: After a turbulent life in London, Rona returns to her childhood home in Scotlands Orkney Islands. Amid wild, rugged beauty, she confronts her troubled past and seeks healing.

programme.title: Longing
programme.desc: Daniel, a wealthy bachelor in his 60s, learns that a former girlfriend gave birth to a child 20 years ago -- and that his son has just died. He starts to reevaluate his life choices as he gets to know his deceased son through those closest to him.

programme.title: The Summit
programme.desc: During a presidential summit in Chile, Argentinas president Hernn Blanco goes through family drama affecting the relationship with his daughter while facing the most important moment in his career.

programme.title: Double Indemnity
programme.desc: An insurance man (Fred MacMurray) helps a platinum blonde (Barbara Stanwyck) kill her husband, but all does not go as planned.

programme.title: Eterno resplandor de una mente sin recuerdos
programme.desc: A doctors invention allows a couple (Jim Carrey, Kate Winslet) to erase the memories of their tumultuous relationship.

programme.title: Quien mato a las Maggie Moores?
programme.desc: Police Chief Sanders investigates the bizarre murders of two women with the same name and unravels a web of small-town lies. He meets and quickly falls for Rita, a nosy neighbor who is eager to help solve the mystery.

programme.title: The 355
programme.desc: CIA agent Mason "Mace" Brown joins forces with a rival German agent, a cutting-edge computer specialist and a Colombian psychologist when a top-secret weapon falls into the hands of a group of mercenaries.

programme.title: Everything Everywhere All at Once
programme.desc: When an interdimensional rupture unravels reality, an unlikely hero must channel her newfound powers to fight bizarre and bewildering dangers from the multiverse.

programme.title: The Settlers
programme.desc: In Chile, three horsemen are paid to protect a vast estate. Accompanying a British soldier and an American mercenary is a mixed-race sniper, who realizes that his true mission is to kill the indigenous population.

programme.title: First Man
programme.desc: Engineer Neil Armstrong spends years in training after joining NASA in the 1960s. On July 16, 1969, the nation and world watch in wonder as Armstrong and fellow astronauts Buzz Aldrin and Michael Collins embark on a historic mission to the moon.

programme.title: I Saw the TV Glow
programme.desc: A classmate introduces teenage Owen to a mysterious late-night TV show -- a vision of a supernatural world beneath their own. In the pale glow of the television, Owens view of reality begins to crack.

programme.desc: As Gercourt furthers his quest to weaken her, Isabelle enlists help in her fight against Paris most powerful man.

programme.title: Next Stop, Christmas
programme.desc: Angie wonders what life would be like if she had married an ex who became famous. When she finds herself magically transported into the past, Angie has the chance to relive that Christmas and learn what (and who) is truly important to her.

programme.title: Christmas in Evergreen
programme.desc: Hoping to spur her longtime beau to action, a small-town veterinarian wishes upon a snow globe that this will be her most romantic Christmas ever.

programme.title: The Christmas Train
programme.desc: A cynical journalist must get from Washington, D.C., to Los Angeles in time for Christmas, and his only option is to take the train.

programme.title: Dr. Seuss How the Grinch Stole Christmas
programme.desc: A curmudgeon (Jim Carrey) living atop Mount Crumpit sets out to quash the yuletide preparations of the Christmas-loving Whos of Whoville. Anthony Hopkins narrates.

programme.title: Tis the Season to Be Merry
programme.desc: Looking for a fresh angle for her book on relationships, Merry heads to snow-covered Vermont. She soon finds a new perspective and Christmas cheer when she meets a charismatic aid worker named Chris.

programme.title: The Christmas Retreat
programme.desc: When Kims boyfriend breaks up with her instead of proposing, Kims mom takes her away to a Christmas retreat to reconnect with the spirit of the holiday. When she gets there, she meets newly unemployed Mark.

programme.title: Where Are You, Christmas?
programme.desc: Addy wishes for a year without Christmas and wakes up in a black-and-white world. She must work together with the town mechanic to restore the holiday to all its glory.

programme.title: Hollywood on Set
programme.desc: Features behind-the-scenes footage from movie sets and discussions with the cast and crew about the details of each film.

programme.title: Hollywood on Set
programme.sub-title: Los Increbles 2; El Legado del Diablo; El To Drew
programme.desc: Features behind-the-scenes footage from movie sets and discussions with the cast and crew about the details of each film.

programme.title: Christmas Wishes and Mistletoe Kisses
programme.desc: Weeks before Christmas, an interior designer is hired to decorate the estate of a wealthy businessman.

programme.title: A Holiday Hideout
programme.desc: An upstanding female private detective named Jessie goes undercover to guard two people in the witness protection program.

programme.title: Christmas Getaway
programme.desc: After a surprising breakup with her boyfriend, a travel writer decides to go on the picturesque Christmas vacation planned for the two of them, alone.

programme.title: Boyfriends of Christmas Past
programme.desc: Marketing executive Lauren must learn to open her heart with the help of four ghosts of ex-boyfriends who visit her leading up to Christmas.

programme.title: A Shoe Addicts Christmas
programme.desc: Department store employee Noelle visits Christmases of past, present and future as her guardian angel helps her navigate her wishes for a connection with her father, her dream career and love.

programme.title: Single and Ready to Jingle
programme.desc: A womans vacation plans go disastrously wrong when she mistakenly winds up in St. John, Alaska, during Christmastime. However, things take a turn for the better when she meets a local man who sweeps her off her feet.

programme.title: The Most Colorful Time of the Year
programme.desc: A colorblind elementary school teacher meets an optometrist who helps bring color into his life in time for the holidays.

programme.title: Project Christmas Wish
programme.desc: A womans life becomes transformed as she works toward granting a little girls wish for a Christmas like she used to have with her mother.

programme.title: Sugarplummed
programme.desc: When Emily wishes for a perfect Christmas like the ones found in the popular Sugarplum movies, shes shocked when Sugarplum herself appears to help her fulfill it.

programme.title: Elf
programme.desc: Adopted as a baby by one of Santas elves (Bob Newhart), a man (Will Ferrell) leaves the workshop to search for his family in New York.

programme.title: A Season for Family
programme.desc: Maddys adopted son, Wesley, has just one wish for Christmas -- to meet his brother, Cody, who was adopted into a different family. Circumstances soon bring the two siblings together while sparks fly between their respective parents.

programme.title: Mystery on Mistletoe Lane
programme.desc: New to town, Heidi Wicks and her kids discover a Christmas mystery in their historic home. Local handyman and historian David helps along the way, finding his own surprising connection.

programme.title: Holiday Date
programme.desc: Brooke is dumped right before Christmas and enlists the help of actor Joel to play the role of her boyfriend for the holidays.

programme.title: Switched for Christmas
programme.desc: At their obligatory pre-Christmas lunch, estranged identical twins decide to swap lives up until Christmas Day.

programme.title: Finding Santa
programme.desc: Jessica is thrilled to be taking over the running of her New England towns Christmas parade. But when the man playing St. Nick falls ill she needs to scramble to find a replacement, even if the replacement is unwilling.

programme.title: My Dads Christmas Date
programme.desc: A 16-year-old tries to play matchmaker for her widowed father during Christmastime.

programme.title: Haul Out the Holly
programme.desc: Emily comes home to visit her parents, only to discover theyre leaving for a trip of their own. While staying at their house for the holidays, Emily meets members of the community who want her to join in the neighborhoods Christmas festivities.

programme.title: Haul Out the Holly: Lit Up
programme.desc: Emily and Jared are looking forward to celebrating the holidays together again, this time as a couple. Theyre also ready to work with members of the community to make this years Christmas festivities the best yet.

programme.title: Mistletoe Match
programme.desc: When Olivia goes under cover to report on the popular annual Mistletoe Match event, she meets Thomas, who is just as skeptical about the event as she is. Sparks fly, but she may risk losing a promotion for the romance she never saw coming.

programme.title: Arthur Christmas
